data.text:
When Eva Green Nunn was born in 1881, in Green, Kentucky, United States, her father, John Anderson Nunn, was 31 and her mother, Sabina Wallace, was 31. She married George Al Martin on 9 June 1895, in Green, Kentucky, United States. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She was buried in Nunn, Crittenden, Kentucky, United States.
